{{Top|leg}}
'''Dead blade''' was a term used by the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] in reference to any non-energized bladed [[Melee weapon/Legends|melee weapon]]. This was in direct contrast to weapons such as [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsabers]], which were in essence entirely energized, and [[Vibroblade/Legends|vibroblades]], which were characterized by their energized vibration, which made them more effective at cutting through various substances. Dead blades were typically only used by primitive cultures or those without high technology.

